title: Type Alias "Adapter" is not defined
body:
**Describe the bug**

The type alias "Adapter" described at [here](https://elizaos.github.io/eliza/api/type-aliases/Adapter/) is not defined in https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/blob/main/packages/core/src/types.ts#L637
